anuary 5, 2012"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p18","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"3-2"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_16","part":"s1p19","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"4."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_15","part":"s1p19","offsets":[{"start":3,"text":"Rent and Method and Time of Payment"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p20","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"4-1"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_9","part":"s1p20","offsets":[{"start":4,"text":"Both parties agree that the daily rent is RMB0.6 per square meter per day and the monthly rent of the Premises is RMB249514. (In capital: RMB TWO HUNDRED AND FORTY NINE THOUSAND AND FIVE HUNDRED AND FOURTEEN) The rent shall remain unchanged during the tenancy."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p21","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"4-2"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_9","part":"s1p21","offsets":[{"start":4,"text":"The rent shall be pre-paid quarterly. The rent for the first quarter shall be paid before Party A handle the Premises to Party B. Afterwards, Party B shall pay the rent before the 15th of the month immediately prior to the next quarter. Party A will issue invoice for the rent of next quarter before 15th of the last month of the last quarter. Party B shall pay the rent within 10 working days after the receipt of the invoice issued by Party A. If Party B fails to pay punctually, for every single day of delay, it shall pay a penalty to Party A at the rate of 0.05% of the monthly rent."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p22","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"4-3"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_16","part":"s1p23","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"5."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_15","part":"s1p23","offsets":[{"start":3,"text":"Deposit and Other Fees"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p24","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"5-1"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_23","part":"s1p24","offsets":[{"start":4,"text":"Both parties agree that Party B shall pay Party A the Deposit equal to the rent of 2 months in an amount of RMB499,028 within 7 days upon the execution of this Contract. On receipt of the Deposit, Party A shall issue a receipt to Party B."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{"f_24":{"value":"guarantee_transferable","confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1}}},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_23","part":"s1p25","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"By termination of the tenancy, Party A shall offset from the Deposit the fees bearable by Party B hereunder and return the remains to Party B without interest."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{"f_24":{"value":"guarantee_transferable","confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1}}},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p26","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"5-2"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_23","part":"s1p26","offsets":[{"start":4,"text":"During the tenancy, Party B shall bear the costs of water, electricity, gas, air-condition, telecom, equipments, property management and land tax relating to the use of the Premises. If the relevant expense is paid by Party A, Party A will charge Party B with the proof of invoice. Party B shall pay an amount of RMB3418 as land tax each month."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{"f_24":{"value":"services_charges","confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1}}},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p27","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"5-3"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_16","part":"s1p28","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"6."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_15","part":"s1p28","offsets":[{"start":3,"text":"Requirements for Using the Premises and Responsibility for Reparation"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p29","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"6-1"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_23","part":"s1p29","offsets":[{"start":4,"text":"During the tenancy, in the event that Party B discovers any damage or breakdown of the Premises and accessory facilities, it shall notify Party A promptly for reparation. Party A shall repair them within 3 days from the date of receipt of the notice. If Party A fails to repair in time, Party B may repair them at the cost of Party A."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{"f_24":{"value":"landlord_repairs","confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1}}},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p30","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"6-2"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p31","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"6-3"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p32","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"6-4"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_16","part":"s1p33","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"7."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_15","part":"s1p33","offsets":[{"start":3,"text":"Conditions of the Premises When Returned"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p34","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"7-1"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_23","part":"s1p34","offsets":[{"start":4,"text":"By the expiration of the tenancy or by the termination of this contract, Party B shall return the Premises to Party A within 10 days of the expiration or termination. If Party B fails to return the Premises punctually without the consent of Party A, it shall pay the rent to Party A during the period of occupation of the Premises. If the delay is over 15 days, Party A may re-enter into the Premises, and Party B is considered to give up the ownership of all the items in the Premises, which Party A may dispose freely."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{"f_24":{"value":"reinstatement_clause","confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1}}},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p35","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"7-2"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_23","part":"s1p35","offsets":[{"start":4,"text":"Party B shall return the Premises in a condition consistent with the Premises having been used normally. Party A shall inspect the Premises when the Premises are returned and the parties hereto shall settle the fees that they are respectively responsible for."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{"f_24":{"value":"reinstatement_clause","confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1}}},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_16","part":"s1p36","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"8."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_15","part":"s1p36","offsets":[{"start":3,"text":"Sublet, Transfer and Exchange"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p37","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"8-1"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_23","part":"s1p37","offsets":[{"start":4,"text":"Party B may sublet part or the whole of the Premises to another party during the tenancy with the written consent of Party A. If Party B sublet the Premises without consent, Party A may inform Party B to terminate this Contract and require Party B to return its benefit from the sublet to Party A."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{"f_24":{"value":"sublease_permitted","confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1}}},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_16","part":"s1p38","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"9."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_15","part":"s1p38","offsets":[{"start":3,"text":"Conditions of Termination of this Contract"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p39","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"9-1"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_18","part":"s1p45","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"9-2"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_23","part":"s1p45","offsets":[{"start":4,"text":"Both parties agree that if any of the following events occurs, either party may inform the other party upon a written notice to terminate this Contract. The defaulting party shall pay the other party a penalty as liquidated damages equal to three times of the monthly rent. If the said liquidate damages are insufficient to make up for the losses suffered by the other party, the defaulting party shall further compensate for the balance thereof:"}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{"f_24":{"value":"break_option","confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1}}},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_23","part":"s1p46","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"(1) Having failed to hand over the Premises punctually, Party A again fails to hand over the same within 15 days from the date of Party B’s written demand."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{"f_24":{"value":"break_option","confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1}}},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_23","part":"s1p47","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"(2) The Premises handed over by Party A fail to comply with the conditions as herein contained, which frustrates the purpose of the lease; or the Premises are defective and endanger the safety of Party B."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{"f_24":{"value":"break_option","confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1}}},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_23","part":"s1p48","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"(3) Party B changes the usage of the Premises without written consent of Party A, which causes damage to the Premises."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{"f_24":{"value":"break_option","confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1}}},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_23","part":"s1p49","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"(4) The main structure of the Premises is damaged at fault of Party B."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{"f_24":{"value":"break_option","confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1}}},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_23","part":"s1p50","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"(5) Party B sublets the Premises, transfers the leasing right of the Premises or exchanges with a third party their respective leased premises without permission."}],"coordinates":[],"confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1},"fields":{"f_24":{"value":"break_option","confidence":{"state":"pre-added","who":["user:terezalat"],"prob":1}}},"normalizations":{}},{"classId":"e_23","part":"s1p51","offsets":[{"start":0,"text":"(6)